From 6e13015209eaabdbb6ba2e5a99e16cd0e5234ce6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 17:54:19 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: unify button naming across all layers + remove inline
 overlay
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

CRITICAL FIX: Button name inconsistency across 4 layers caused A/X/Y/B,
LB/RB, LT/RT to not be detected in GamepadTester and not mapped correctly
in NativeGamepadMapper.

Layer 1 (GamepadPlugin.kt): emits 'A', 'B', 'X', 'Y', 'LB', 'RB', 'LT', 'RT'
Layer 2 (defaults.ts): uses 'A', 'B', 'X', 'Y', 'RT', 'LT', 'LB', 'RB' ✅
Layer 3 (ButtonPalette.tsx): was using 'BUTTON_A', 'BUTTON_L1', etc ❌
Layer 4 (GamepadTester.tsx kMap): was expecting 'BUTTON_A', 'L1', etc ❌

Fix 1 (GamepadTester.tsx): Updated kMap to match GamepadPlugin output:
  A→a, B→b, X→x, Y→y, LB→l_shoulder, RB→r_shoulder,
  LT→lt_trigger, RT→rt_trigger, L3→l3, R3→r3,
  START→start, SELECT→select, HOME→home, DPAD_*→d_*
  All 17 button names now mapped correctly.

Fix 2 (ButtonPalette.tsx): Changed all mappedKey from 'BUTTON_A' to 'A',
  'BUTTON_L1' to 'LB', 'BUTTON_R1' to 'RB', 'BUTTON_L2' to 'LT',
  'BUTTON_R2' to 'RT', 'BUTTON_L3' to 'L3', 'BUTTON_R3' to 'R3',
  'BUTTON_SELECT' to 'SELECT', 'BUTTON_START' to 'START',
  'BUTTON_M1' to 'M1', 'BUTTON_M2' to 'M2'.
  Now matches defaults.ts and GamepadPlugin output.

Fix 3 (App.tsx): Removed inline OverlayWysiwyg rendering when overlayActive.
  This was a duplicate of the native FloatingOverlayService overlay.
  The web overlay (z-[9999] pointer-events-none) was covering the screen
  and interfering with the native overlay service.
  Native overlay is handled by FloatingOverlayService.java which creates
  a separate WebView window — no need for inline web overlay.
---
 src/App.tsx                      | 13 -------------
 src/components/ButtonPalette.tsx | 28 ++++++++++++++--------------
 src/components/GamepadTester.tsx | 13 +++++++++----
 3 files changed, 23 insertions(+), 31 deletions(-)

